<script setup>
import { useNotesStore } from '@/store/index'
import { onMounted } from 'vue';
import { useRoute } from 'vue-router'
import { ref } from 'vue'

const route = useRoute()
const id = ref(route.params.id)

onMounted(() => {
  useNotesStore().getNote(id.value)
})


</script>

<template>
  
</template>
